04/26/17


 Summary ToggleBoston Beer Reports First Quarter 2017 Results
 BOSTON , April 26, 2017 /PRNewswire/ -- The Boston Beer Company, Inc. (NYSE: SAM) reported first quarter 2017 net revenue of $161.7 million , a decrease of $27.1 million or 14% from the same period last year, mainly due to a decline in shipments of 15%, partially offset by price increases. 
READ MORE
 


