Boston Beer Company - Wikipedia






















 






Boston Beer Company

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Boston Beer Company





Type

Public


Traded as
NYSE: SAM
S&P 400 Component


Industry
Alcoholic beverage


Founded
1984


Founders
Jim Koch, Rhonda Kallman[1]


Headquarters
Boston, MA (Administrative Offices and Brewery)



Key people

Jim Koch
Chairman
